headline: Gallagher's Billion-Dollars Gambit: Latest Deal Shakes Up the Insurance World
summary: Fresh Midwest expansion and a $13.45B acquisition position Gallagher as the industry's unstoppable force.

headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Afina Insurance Advisors, Inc.
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of Oakbrook Terrace, Illinois-based Afina Insurance Advisors Inc. (Afina Insurance). Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
